		<a class="float-right italic" href="/en/guides/" hreflang="en-ca">English</a>
		<h1>Skoolie <small>Guides pour compléter le projet</small></h1>
		<div class="my-4 alert alert-info">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="stroke-current shrink-0 w-6 h-6"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
			<span class="text-xl">{description}</span>
			<a href="/details/" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">Détails</a>
		</div>

		<ol>
			<li><a href="https://quebecskoolie.com/">quebec skoolie</a></li>
			<li><a href="https://campeurs-skoolie.com/">campeurs-skoolie</a></li>
			<li><a href="https://skooliecanada.ca/">skoolie canada</a></li>
		</ol>
	</main>
</Layout>
